      <title>俄罗斯联邦储蓄银行季度利润因拨备增加而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-sberbank-reports-marginal-drop-third-quarter-profits-2024-10-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯主要银行俄罗斯联邦储蓄银行周四公布第三季度利润小幅下降至 4111 亿卢布（42 亿美元），原因是贷款增长放缓，且利率飙升导致拨备增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-sberbank-reports-marginal-drop-third-quarter-profits-2024-10-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
