      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/caixabanks-lending-income-hit-by-lower-rates-unveils-share-buyback-2024-10-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙 Caixabank 银行第三季度的贷款收入因利率下降而承受压力，尽管该行由于控制了融资成本而重申了 2024 年高个位数增长预期。]]></description>
